      "review_title": "Great for future tradies",
      "review_description": "Really nice work on self-guided onboarding and interactions. The watch-instructor is great. Even the tradies that appear on the phone are very lifelike. I went to a plumbing training facility a few years ago that had a massive piping structure on-site that cost many millions of dollars, isn't portable and isn't anywhere near as immersive (eg - how VR creates a pseudo sense-memory of electrocution and other high-stakes scenarios). Insane that more plumbers aren't being trained like this.",
